# dev_backend (T3) populates this directory per the architect spec module table:
#
#   concept_queue.py       — pick next concept; flock-guarded mutations
#   corpus_loader.py       — PD-licensed quote excerpts for a concept
#   script_gen.py          — soul.md + concept + excerpts → script.json
#   tts.py                 — per-turn ElevenLabs API calls
#   stitch.py              — ffmpeg concat
#   normalize.py           — ffmpeg-normalize --preset podcast (two-pass)
#   artifacts.py           — show_notes.md, citations.jsonl, pacing.json
#                            (fail-fast license guard inside)
#   publish.py             — R2 upload + feed.xml regen
#                            (HALT guard: refuses Ep001 unless DHARMA_EP001_APPROVED=1)
#   tg_notify.py           — tg_send.sh wrapper
#
# Target: each module ≤ 200 LOC.
